CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper June 29, 1946, pg. 21, reads: "Plan Prom - Putting the finishing touches to plans for the Centre Avenue YMCA's annual graduation prom on Friday, June 28, are members of the committee, left to right: Madeline Swan, Elaine Davis, Harold Keith, Clifford Allen and Dolores Wilson. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Madeline Sharpe Swan (Foggie), Elaine Davis, Harold Keith seated at desk, Clifford Allen, and Dolores Wilson gathered for graduation prom planning committee meeting, Centre Avenue YMCA
